I/D polymorphism of ACE gene is the most frequent examined polymorphism and 
probably very strongly connected to pathology. The majority of studies describe 
negative influence of allele D on frequency and course of given diseases. The 
result of negative effect of this allele should be visible in people with long 
life expectancy. To answer the question: is I/D polymorphism ACE gene 
