used polymerase chain reaction methods. The results were calculated using the 
programme Statistica 5.1 PL. One used the independent chi 2 test and Odds Ratio 
to compare the genotype map and localisation of alleles. After having made 
comparative examination no connection was made between I/D polymorphism ACE gene 
and long-life.

